1.0.name: wordpress/levelfourstorefront
1.0.description:
WordPress Plugin Shopping Cart Simple install into new or existing WordPress blogs. Customers purchase directly from your store! Get a full E-Commerce platform in WordPress! Sell products, downloadable goods, gift cards, clothing and more! And now with WordPress, the powerful features are still very easy to administrate!

Level Four provides FREE administrative software, so there is no need to use WordPress as a slow management system for your products. Desktop PC, Mac, iPad, and Android software is freely available to download and allows you to control the myriad of options the software has to offer.
